            "type": "Text",
            "text": "🛡️ Identity Verification Required\n\nTo ensure the security of your account and comply with financial regulations, we need to verify your identity.\n\nThis process is:\n✅ Secure and encrypted\n✅ Takes 2-3 minutes\n✅ Required only once\n✅ Bank-grade security\n\nYou'll need:\n📄 Government-issued ID\n📱 Phone for photos\n📍 Current address proof"
